    "name": "I Need To Go",
    "steam_appid": 3327280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/85772aa3dd19c8188fbf240b9b0c6e04.avif?t=1772041409\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A nostalgic point-and-click adventure game inspired by the classics!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story filled with humor and emotion, coupled with interesting puzzles that evoke nostalgia, laughter and thought.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the naive Eddie, a metalhead who seems a bit lost in life. Eddie's memories are fuzzy and his better half, Lisa, is nowhere to be found. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Where is she and why does it seem like everyone is losing their memories? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the help of a magical figure, guide him through a mysterious, ruined but still beautiful world in the search for love and answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet interesting, weird and funny characters, find what you've lost or lose what you've found.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/60a6a0aeb831840051657d8fb13cb620.poster.avif?t=1772041409\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/60a6a0aeb831840051657d8fb13cb620.webm?t=1772041409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/60a6a0aeb831840051657d8fb13cb620.mp4?t=1772041409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/02c869cafa8062c6f0852f77d807b490.avif?t=1772041409\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story</strong>: Follow Eddie on his strange, humorous, but also somber journey to find answers in this nostalgic point-and-click adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>World</strong>: A strange yet familiar place that holds mysteries for you and Eddie to unwrap.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Soundtrack: </strong>A heartfelt soundtrack and of course, there will be rock!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice Acting</strong>: 100% voiced for your immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixel Art</strong>: Using a similar resolution to the classics and turning the old limitations of the past into stylistic choices.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interface</strong>: Inspired by the classics with all the verbs one could ever need!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles</strong>: That make sense, mostly. Just kidding, they totally make sense.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/34171a415c28f2a98994419979addd33.poster.avif?t=1772041409\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/34171a415c28f2a98994419979addd33.webm?t=1772041409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327280/extras/34171a415c28f2a98994419979addd33.mp4?t=1772041409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
